{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4815fbba71","title":"右派言论——“肃反由于斯大林的影响是扩大化了”","origin":"《南开大学右派反动言论选集》（天津：南开大学社会主义思想教育教研室，1957年9月）。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"2b1bbe0b72","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"4815fbba71"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"bc10d795d5","name":"张炳泉"},{"id":"f2840d39f9","name":"南开大学"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"6a0f49d6b4","type":"title","text":"右派言论——“肃反由于斯大林的影响是扩大化了”","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4815fbba71"},{"id":"2a0a95b84c","type":"authors","text":"南开大学张炳泉","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4815fbba71"},{"id":"c9e392528a","type":"subtitle","text":"[张炳泉：南开大学数学系学生]","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4815fbba71"},{"id":"2f48db64ee","type":"paragraph","text":"“党中央不该提出不冤枉一个好人的方针而应该提出宁肯错斗多少，不愿放走一个的方针。”","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4815fbba71"},{"id":"04efa7a4f2","type":"paragraph","text":"“肃反的成绩也可以说是主要的，因为只要肃出了一个反革命来，就算是达到了目的，不管这当中起了多大的副作用。肃反要达到目的可以看作是直径，副作用可以看作是横切面，只要到了直径的顶点，横的方面有多大都可以不管。又好像作实验一样，只要做出了结果，可以不管用了多少材料，有多少副作用。”","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4815fbba71"},{"id":"b092463990","type":"paragraph","text":"“中国的肃反问题，由于斯大林的影响是扩大化了。”","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4815fbba71"},{"id":"7369faed83","type":"paragraph","text":"“肃反刺伤了许多人的心灵，肃反的结果是使人与人之间不敢说真话了。”","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4815fbba71"}],"page":{"id":"2c959f5048","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"4815fbba71","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}